snippet.title: Chess Ultra | Announce Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Immerse yourself in the stunning world of Chess Ultra. Find out more at: www.playchessultra.com
Coming to PS4 Pro and PSVR this Spring, Chess Ultra is the best looking chess game in the world. Featuring a variety of game modes, and intuitive online play, this is the only chess game you need.
